WEBVTT

00:02.169 --> 00:04.171
Hira's dead, David.

00:04.171 --> 00:06.465
Yes, she's dead.

00:06.465 --> 00:08.383
Hira took a bullet that's it. Game over.

00:08.383 --> 00:09.968
We move on.

00:12.888 --> 00:14.765
You made her feel ashamed.

00:14.765 --> 00:16.975
You!

00:16.975 --> 00:19.269
You...

00:19.269 --> 00:20.395
Seen the game the other night?

00:20.395 --> 00:22.397
Yeah, what, Biriliski went through the boards?

00:22.397 --> 00:23.190
Yeah. I think it's..

00:23.190 --> 00:25.275
- Oh man, you're not...
- Why? You think that's dangerous?

00:25.275 --> 00:28.195
I don't think. I know.

00:28.195 --> 00:31.865
Got a situation developing in the States
related to a prion type disease.

00:31.865 --> 00:33.575
- Prion?
- Mad cow.

00:33.575 --> 00:34.993
- It's bullshit.
- I'm sorry?

00:34.993 --> 00:37.996
It takes at least 7 years
for a prion protein to fuck up the brain

00:37.996 --> 00:40.374
ans at least another year
after that before you die.

00:40.374 --> 00:44.378
She had this disease, something
only 60 or 70 year old people get.

00:44.378 --> 00:46.171
Old people, you know.

00:46.171 --> 00:49.299
Why? Why did this happen to my baby?

00:49.299 --> 00:51.677
How many people are we talking about?

00:51.677 --> 00:56.390
How many people ate a piece of chicken,
an egg, or got a flu shot lately?

