29:15.881 --> 29:17.799
I uhh.. put some close on.

29:21.678 --> 29:25.098
Oh, thank you. Thank you for coming.

29:25.098 --> 29:27.476
I didn't really have much
of a choice there, Harv.

29:27.476 --> 29:29.478
FBI thinks
