29:56.880 --> 30:00.300
Well, sure. That's why I did it.

30:04.012 --> 30:06.098
Can't fix it 'til it's broken, is that it?

30:06.098 --> 30:08.600
Yeah. Yeah.

30:08.600 --> 30:10.602
You see.

30:10.602 --> 30:14.481
Prions, those little tiny proteins
can destroy us all.

30:14.481 --> 30:18.110
They're like a virus, a cancer.

30:18.110 --> 30:19.987
And I can cure them all.

30:19.987 --> 30:21.113
I know how.

30:21.113 --> 30:23.991
You want to tell that to the mother
