30:23.991 --> 30:26.910
No. That wasn't suppose to happen.

30:26.910 --> 30:31.915
I was gonna expose the prions in the Wide Valley
chicken and then show them I have a cure.

30:31.915 --> 30:35.377
You don't know that, Harvey.
