30:40.883 --> 30:43.177
You have the samples, don't you?

30:43.177 --> 30:45.095
They took them. Didn't they tell you?

30:45.095 --> 30:48.098
They didn't tell me anything
except you wanted to see me.

30:48.098 --> 30:50.601
I was bringing them to you,
so you could see it for yourself.

30:50.601 --> 30:51.393
You could test them.

30:51.393 --> 30:52.895
Oh, I'd love to have a look at them.

30:52.895 --> 30:57.608
And you'll see, and they'll have to
refinance my study, because I can save them.

30:57.608 --> 30:59.401
Sure you can, Harvey.

30:59.401 --> 31:03.989
