31:28.514 --> 31:30.807
I want to talk to you.

31:30.807 --> 31:32.976
Hey, David's back in town.

31:32.976 --> 31:34.686
How was the windy city?

31:34.686 --> 31:35.312
Ah..

31:35.312 --> 31:37.898
It was..

31:37.898 --> 31:40.692
