31:40.692 --> 31:43.695
Well, that for me to know
and you'll find out.

31:43.695 --> 31:44.488
Here.

31:44.488 --> 31:47.282
The missing prion samples,
courtesy of the FBI.

31:47.282 --> 31:49.493
We need to run those,
match 'em to what we've got.

31:49.493 --> 31:51.411
