32:36.582 --> 32:39.793
- Miss Richmond, please.
- Bob.

32:39.793 --> 32:43.505
I have to go. Goodbye.

32:50.804 --> 32:52.097
You okay?

32:52.097 --> 32:53.891
Why?

32:53.891 --> 32:55.517
