That's why he exhibited
chest pains, signs of fatigue, dizziness.

33:19.917 --> 33:23.587
He said it because professional athletes
are used to working through their pain.

33:23.587 --> 33:25.589
Ah.. You speak bullshit too.

33:25.589 --> 33:27.216
Na, it's like a second language to me.

33:27.216 --> 33:29.092
Did you specifically ask about the doping?

33:29.092 --> 33:32.804
Oh, Biriliski passed every single test
the League threw at him.

33:32.804 --> 33:35.307
You know about this
Bioxene growth hormone?

33:35.307 --> 33:37.184
I'm working with Bob on it.

33:37.184 --> 33:39.394
We got a Bioxene growth hormones structure

33:39.394 --> 33:40.896
and we looked for the same thing in Danny.

33:40.896 --> 33:42.814
This is what we got.

33:42.814 --> 33:46.109
- Something very similar.
- Ah.. but different.

33:46.109 --> 33:49.279
So the stuff that Danny took
is not the Bioxene product?

33:49.279 --> 33:51.907
What's in his blood is a highly sialilated

33:51.907 --> 33:55.077
but mutated version of
