with gene therapy?

34:13.178 --> 34:15.304
No, but I obviously somebody else has.

34:15.304 --> 34:17.516
The muscle growth hormone in Danny
had to be concocted in a lab.

34:17.516 --> 34:21.311
Instead of injecting something into him
that shouldn't be there,

34:21.311 --> 34:22.603
he gets his body to make it.

34:22.603 --> 34:25.815
One injection of the DNA
and his body makes the hormone.

34:25.815 --> 34:28.402
So he's not cheating. His body is.

34:28.402 --> 34:31.112
