35:35.385 --> 35:38.514
What can we do for those
who are potentially infected?

35:38.514 --> 35:40.182
There's nothing we can do.

35:40.182 --> 35:41.308
There is no cure.

35:41.308 --> 35:44.603
There is one thing.

35:44.603 --> 35:48.398
You could fund Harvey Thomas' research.
Let him pick up where he left off.

35:48.398 --> 35:50.817
He's not just ahead of the curve on this.
